-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07BJJzw.jpg&h=265d35b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法官陳嘉信<br />\n2017年已經企喺警暴戈邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:03:27.000Z","msg":"但係就今次正係睇法理依據  中大入稟人無乜機會勝出 因為佢要推翻常理 就係警員無論咩事入私人地方都要搜查令或事先得到業主同意 咁以後你係街上比人打劫強姦都好 警員只可係公眾地方追捕 只要個賊入左私人地方 就要停一停 諗一諗"},{"pid":"e5d75c1ab9fdc5e4dd061c8fbe50c0a496e47e03","tid":1718163,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"843e94b59fc7d00c0c5684f62e123e420425ac4a","tid":1718163,"uid":61405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b773924d37ddb29122e20f72efcc1533b081eb3","tid":1718163,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"照個官咁講其實狗隻俱樂部都可以係非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢有作出挑撥行為擾亂或意圖擾亂社會安寧 就係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:04:42.000Z","msg":"之前有隻狗拎個BARBELL出黎恐嚇市民算唔算"},{"pid":"1c5880799d9cfc1ba9d888efba153b52a14203d3","tid":1718163,"uid":61405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f8c2332f4c46126748cc6a6932eff9fd2f71393","tid":1718163,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"843e94b59fc7d00c0c5684f62e123e420425ac4a","tid":1718163,"uid":61405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b773924d37ddb29122e20f72efcc1533b081eb3","tid":1718163,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"照個官咁講其實狗隻俱樂部都可以係非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"如果佢有作出挑撥行為擾亂或意圖擾亂社會安寧 就係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"萬人屌老母都唔算?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:05:23.000Z","msg":"萬人屌完老母 有無車行唔到或任何實質社會影響 除左你心情差左外"},{"pid":"794583f0d59964283578a4f62d7b7bafa067d083","tid":1718163,"uid":61405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d75c1ab